defaultinvest in innovation and innovative new technologies. There is a strong business case for that, as the industries themselves are fast changing due to developing technologies. Innova
defaulttion also comes with the need for
default new skillsets, therefore investment in te
defaultchnology should also consider investment in industry-wide training and n
defaultew pathways. In our opinion the BBC should
default play their part in this.
